{"lemma":"غِلْظَةٍ","slug":"غِلْظَةٍ","root":"غ.ل.ظ","root_slug":"غ-ل-ظ","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ل-ظ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غِلْظَة","root":"غلظ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32262","n32263","n32264"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%90%D9%84%D9%92%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32262","headword_ar":"غَلْظَةٌ","root":"glZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n32263","headword_ar":"غُلْظَةٌ","root":"glZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n32264","headword_ar":"غِلْظَةٌ","root":"glZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guloZapN","text_ar":"غُلْظَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galoZapN","text_ar":"غَلْظَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1: these three forms are mentioned by Zj, (TA,) and in the Bári', (Msb, TA,) on the authority of IAar, (Msb,) and by Sgh; but the first of them [only] is commonly known: (TA:) they are substs. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galuZa","text_ar":"غَلُظَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thickness, grossness, bigness, bulkiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coarseness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Roughness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ruggedness."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riq~apN","text_ar":"رِقَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in manners, disposition, action"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conduct, speech, life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"roughness, coarseness, rudeness, unkindness, hardness, churlishness, incivility, surliness, roughness in manners, hardness to deal with, incompliance, unobsequiousness, evilness of disposition, illnature,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb: *) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an affair. (TA, as shown by an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiyZN","text_ar":"غَلِيظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN fiyhi giloZapN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ فِيهِ غِلْظَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man in whom is roughness, coarseness, rudeness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; (S, Msb; *) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAZapN","text_ar":"غِلَاظَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) And it is said in the Kur [ix. 124],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waloyajiduwA fiykumo giloZapN","text_ar":"وَلْيَجِدُوا فِيكُمْ غِلْظَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the last word is pronounced in the three different ways shown above, accord. to different readers; meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And let them find in you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence, and superiority in fight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence, and patient endurance of fight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemence, in enmity and in fight and in making captives."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumaA giloZapN","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمَا غِلْظَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Between them two is enmity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hostility;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugaAlaZapN","text_ar":"مُغَالَظَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IDrd, K.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Msb","Bd"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}